Accompanied a friend to the local hospital to treat a burn they got cooking.  The hospital was clean and decent but I must say I really don't want to go to the hospital in China. So many peoples and no matter what it was a line for this and then for that. Line for appointment, line for schedule, line for pay, line for treatment. Perhaps I am too used to getting things really quickly. When in China one has to just get used to waiting in lines for everything.  That said they are quite modern you can schedule online and pay online now as well as a host of other services done via your cell phone.  #china #hospital #medical #china #panyu #guangdong

Crazy nights partying in China this was the night of the show your chest contest,  I had actually brought a friend who was used to life in the countryside out to the bar and he was shocked by the difference between his small town life and what he saw that night in the club. But another year or two in the big city Shenzhen and he fit right in with the wild partying and such.. In fact I actually ended up excusing myself from his party in later years cause it was just too crazy for my tastes.  China is the land of fun when it comes to going out and having a good time.  Start off about 11 or 12 at night and party away until 5 or 6 or sometimes later in the morning if you know the right places to go to.  #china🇨🇳 #chinatravel #party #drinking #nightclub #guangdong #shenzhen #insearchofchina #china #guangdong #igdaily #instagood #loves_china #red❤️ #asia #people #igasia
